  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "SPA MANAGER",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a <strong>Spa Manager</strong> to join our team!</p><p>As a <strong>Spa Manager</strong>, we rely on you to:</p><ul><li>Responsible for the daily operation of the spa, creating a relaxing caring and personalized spa environment in accordance with the hotel's standards</li><li>Ensure spa facilities, operations and service delivery are of the highest standard at all times</li><li>Supervise and direct the spa team</li><li>Handle all guest requests in a timely, professional and efficient manner</li><li>Familiarize with the spa packages, facilities and equipment and note preferences of guests</li></ul><p>We are looking for someone who:</p><ul><li>Has a passion for wellness and holistic health</li><li>Has certifications from CIDESCO, ITEC, CIBTAC, IFA or equivalent qualification</li><li>Preferably has experience working in either a spa or a hotel background</li><li>In-depth knowledge of spa operations, including an understanding of various spa treatments</li><li>Adaptable to industry trends and changing market demands</li><li>Competence in financial management and experience in revenue maximization through effective sales and marketing strategies for spa packages</li><li>Strong skills in people management and development</li><li>Excellent planning, multitasking and time management</li><li>Excellent decision-making and problem-solving skills</li><li>Has strong interpersonal skills</li><li>Is able to work independently</li></ul><p><strong>We Offer</strong></p><ul><li>5-day work week</li><li>Learning and Development opportunities for career development</li><li>Medical and insurance coverage</li></ul>",
